  DISEASES & MEDICINE
============================================================

Disease:     Tuberculosis
Type:        Bacterial
Pathogen:    M. tuberculosis
Transmission:Airborne droplets
Symptoms:    Persistent cough, night sweats
Treatment:   6-9 month antibiotics
Deaths/yr:   1.6M
Vaccine:     Yes (BCG, partial)
Discovered:  1882

Disease:     Polio
Type:        Viral
Pathogen:    Poliovirus
Transmission:Fecal-oral
Symptoms:    Paralysis in severe cases
Treatment:   No cure; supportive care
Deaths/yr:   0M
Vaccine:     Yes (near-eradicated)
Discovered:  1840

Disease:     Diabetes Type 2
Type:        Metabolic
Pathogen:    Non-communicable
Transmission:Lifestyle
Symptoms:    Thirst, frequent urination, fatigue
Treatment:   Metformin, lifestyle, insulin
Deaths/yr:   1.5M
Vaccine:     No
Discovered:  1922

